=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195780/extras/Resource_management_feature.png?t=1733911997\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195780/extras/ClassOfHeroes_Treasure.gif?t=1733911997\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Broken sword? Shiny coin? From priceless treasures to worthless trash; manage your dungeon haul, sell for some sweet coin or save for another adventure. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195780/extras/get_crafting_feature.png?t=1733911997\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195780/extras/ClassOfHeroes_Recipes.gif?t=1733911997\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From power stones to war hammers, the vast number of recipes alongside the flexible alchemy system allows you to transform items found in the labyrinths, or customise your current weapons attributes.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","developers":["Zerodiv"],"genres":[{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195780/header.jpg?t=1733911997","is_free":false,"legal_notice":"\u00a92024 ACQUIRE Corp. All Rights Reserved. Published by PQube Limited.","linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257018321,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_tra